title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Festive Apparel, Gifts, and More
content:
The holidays have commenced in GTA Online, with festive apparel now appearing in clothing stores throughout Southern San Andreas alongside trees and decorations going up at local landmarks and inside your owned properties — including tasteful holiday décor inside your lavish new mansion property.

Play anytime from December 23 through January 7 to receive an assortment of holiday goodies, including new gifts like the Season’s Greetings Sweater and New Year Fireworks Bodysuit.
